p>\ud83d\udc49<a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/GWbqPY1S6x\">https:\/\/t.co\/GWbqPY1S6x<\/a> <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/YXeKPTc05L\">pic.twitter.com\/YXeKPTc05L<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u2014 Carrefour (@CarrefourGroup) <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/CarrefourGroup\/status\/1511395831240445955?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 5, 2022<\/a><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>Each of the <strong>voxelated NFBEEs will represent a mix of cute insect features<\/strong>, along with the food plants they spend their lives tending to, and in accordance with its worthy mission, Carrefour will donate 100% of all funds raised to the BEEFUND arm of the <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/Fondationfrance\">Foundation De France<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>In addition to the wonderful NFBEE collection, Carrefour will also build its own grand venue in The Sandbox. A supermarket styled temple dedicated to bee-kind and the preserving of bio-diversity. As a result, Carrefour will prepare a bee-themed experience for the Sandbox Alpha Season 4, coming to the metaverse this summer.<\/p>\n<p>The decline of the world\u2019s bee population is no laughing matter. So, any help for these most honourable members of the insect kingdom represents a cause to celebrate.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Find out more &gt;&gt; <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/nft.carrefour.com\/nfbee\/index.html\">Here<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><b>Want more? Connect with NFT Plazas<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/mailchi.mp\/ecadf05eb1bf\/1\">Join the Weekly Newsletter<br \/><\/a><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/qSQwMaM\">Join our Discord<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/nftplazas\">Follow us on Twitter<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopene